Class Profiler

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class Profiler
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel

This class can be seen as a logger class for numeric data in tuple form (like java.util.logging is for text messages)
